{"type": "article", "id": 45664, "title": "这块防渗透毛巾，还能卷成自动贴合的小包｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-09-28T23:05:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 44013, "name": "Tronnovate"}, {"id": 44421, "name": "Beaverhausen"}, {"id": 3208, "name": "Normann Copenhagen"}, {"id": 44422, "name": "ANGEL visual integration"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 92, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170928182246wfMZQ0DOJa1pluLo.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p6 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font-kerning: none; color: #363636} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。<br></p><h3>STIKY by Tronnovate</h3><p>还记得那个模仿布包裹，只要轻轻一包就能完成收纳的轻质背包 <a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/39039.html\">FLATPAC</a> 吗？它背后来自台湾的设计团队 <a href=\"https://www.tronnovate.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Tronnovate</a> 最近又开发了一款名为 STIKY 的多功能织布，它既是一张毛巾，也可像 FLATPAC 一样用作收纳袋。STIKY 这个名字来源于专利的黏贴特性，不需要额外使用别针、只要轻轻一卷就能贴合在一起。它还具有锁水功能，能够让另一面维持干燥，因此可以直接用来打包湿掉的衣物。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1820164289/stiky-fabrics-with-self-adhesiveness-and-amazing-f\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，售价从 18 美元起，分为三种尺寸。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928182347fU9uFC52gLcJW0r1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928182348brc9ZhwHmKUuNlAj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561765\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928182349RtG8mLHaP27nJiOw.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.546875\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928182350HkF7CTiAw9M5UexB.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.546875\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928182354VI2vbJ0UmPtW3haj.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.546875\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Ichinisan by Beaverhausen</h3><p>喜欢稀奇古怪的木制摆件？比利时双人设计工作室 <a href=\"http://www.beaverhausen.be/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Beaverhausen</a> 为丹麦家居品牌 <a href=\"https://www.normann-copenhagen.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Normann Copenhagen</a> 打造的 Ichinisan 系列或许会凭借它们可爱的造型让你嘴角上扬。它们名字源于日语中的一二三，领头老大 Ichi 是一只身材高大的企鹅；身为鹦鹉的老二 Ni 则有着醒目的长喙；知更鸟 San 看起来圆滚滚的。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.normann-copenhagen.com/products/ichi?v=100178\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 74 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928182416iTBAJXVCZtzj6LGW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928182415WtsLD2gROyBM3eZI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928182415XtKxECL420mFncHN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928182415LUcw1IOQGnje6ySo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Marshmallow Wagashi by Tsurutama</h3><p>外观考究的日本和菓子和棉花糖的组合会是什么样？来自冈山县、最早研发棉花糖和菓子的老牌和菓子店<a href=\"http://www.shimoyama.org/\" rel=\"nofollow\">つるの玉子本舗</a>最近就为这一特别的甜点单独创立了名为<a href=\"https://tsurutama.jp/\" rel=\"nofollow\">つるたま</a>（Tsurutama）的品牌。无论是双色羊羹、芝麻馒头还是果酱，都采用天然材料由工匠手工制成，柔和的颜色看起来也很赏心悦目。如果你感兴趣的话，可以通过它的<a href=\"https://shop.tsurutama.jp/\" rel=\"nofollow\">官方网站</a>购买。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928182431mCMF135uL8oGO6A4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928182431kcRnNx0bd7XVy4r1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928182431dagwCSkj0qJAP5Vl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928182432dYlwQtr9yS24vZXM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928182432jM5cqipD4fRLPSkU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Protein project by Tessa Silva-Dawson</h3><p>在生产乳制品的过程中，会产生大量的脱脂牛奶，除去出售的一部分以外，还有很多脱脂牛奶面临着被浪费的命运。为了减少浪费，毕业于英国皇家艺术学院的 Tessa Silva-Dawson 将这些废弃的牛奶转化成酪蛋白塑料，随后加入染料，打造成一批有机陶器。由于它和奶酪的加工过程颇为相似，这也意味着现有的奶酪工厂可以同时进行这种环保材料的生产。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928182444w3cDXqa8f5dnZv7r.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714744\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928182444jzfJdHKOosrEmeVl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.424145\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928182444DMTxJrayeWXQiNm4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.767094\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928182444YxISegE13cyMb4lh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.964744\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>SECRETEA by ANGEL visual integration</h3><p>台湾茶叶品牌<a href=\"http://secretea.qdm.com.tw/\" rel=\"nofollow\">小叶觅蜜</a>在舞鹤地区经营着采用自然农法种植的茶园，由于不使用化学药剂，夏季会有不少小叶绿蝉攀附在茶芽上叮咬，使得茶香也因此变得更浓郁。为了体现茶叶的天然属性，台湾视觉设计工作室 <a href=\"http://www.anglebrand.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">ANGEL visual integration</a> 为其更新了整个视觉系统。设计团队采用了偏女性化的配色风格，使用了大量的粉色以展现“蜜香”这一概念。品牌的新 logo 由优雅流畅的线条构成，选取自英文名中的 S、T 和“茶”三个字符。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928182453uacXCVQw8nKoSsvh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.840596\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928182453PEcmTp69vSGuBRD2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201709281824533q1LNrXkbhtuxQ0I.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928182453qRgH1bwWsONveZr7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Hot Exhibition by Alper Dostal</h3><p>假如博物馆的空调不再运转，会造成什么样的后果？奥地利数码设计师 Alper Dostal 大胆地想象了一个空调失效、热度导致著名画作全部溶化的世界，并将其命名为 Hot Exhibition：《星空》、《呐喊》以及蒙德里安的格子画等都未能幸免。如果你对这种神奇的画展感兴趣，可以通过<a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/54832001/Hot-Exhibition\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>查看全部作品。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928182546GWiDJ8kjqHzt1BZL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.003667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928182545z7K4DmRyg0hx9GZ2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.903423\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928182545siSd03RrtaqbpLT8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.997555\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170928182545VcGq1eMk6ixAaDgl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.888753\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}